	//
	//	NOTE:
	//	Max range = (Max range high << 8) | Max range low
	//	Unit: 0x02 -> (ppm and mg/m3) or 0x04 (ppb and ug/m3)
	//	Signs: 0 (positive) or 1 (negative)
	//	Decimal places: the maximum number of decimal places is 3 (three prim. prev.)
